Triceps is an experimental CEP (Complex Event Processing) engine. It implements
the event stream processing as a library embeddable in C++ and Perl. 

For the build instructions, see BUILD.

For the documentation see doc/. It will be gradually written up as a blog at
http://babkin-cep.blogspot.com/ and collected in doc/.

To contact the author, write to babkin@users.sf.net.

The project home at SourceForge is located at 
http://sourceforge.net/projects/triceps/
